Text: Sounds horrible distorted and warped not worth listening to. But thanks for the upload anyways.

Here's a perfect example of why epic sounding music like this shouldn't be leaked it just gives it a bad name instantly especially to people who don't have the ear of music... This is a rough cut at best and whoever leaked it probably didn't have time to check the dB level on it. Either way this track will be dope as fuck when its all done. Also Alex Da Kidd said in an interview that it's on the Detox album, Dre came to him and asked him to produce it.

This song isn't bad at all, I really like it. It's different, and different is exactly what this industry needs right now. I hope Detox will bring some new ideas to the table. I've been waiting for this album since friggin high school. I completely forgot about it actually. From what I've read, it will be released this month, finally!
